    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my reliable ride, and it\u2019s looking for a great new home! It\u2019s been super well-maintained and is still in wonderful shape, making it perfect for your daily commutes or fun weekend getaways. It runs like a dream and is totally ready to hit the road with its next owner. Come take it for a spin\u2014I just know you're going to love how it handles!",
