    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of performance and reliability. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, though closer inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small, superficial scratch on the rear passenger door\u2014typical for a car that has been enjoyed on the road. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean; the leather seats have been regularly conditioned and show only light bolster wear on the driver's side. All electronics, including the infotainment system and dual-zone climate control, function perfectly. Mechanically, this car is sound. It has been serviced every 5,000 miles with full synthetic oil, and the brakes and tires were replaced within the last year. It shifts smoothly and handles with the precision you'd expect from a well-cared-for model. I have kept a folder of all maintenance receipts to provide the next owner with complete peace of mind.",
      "price": 36500.0,
