    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m looking to find a new home for this absolute gem. It\u2019s been super reliable and has been taken such good care of\u2014it\u2019s honestly in great shape and ready for its next adventure! Whether you're commuting or road-tripping, this ride won't let you down. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I know the next owner will love it just as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
