    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies. This example benefits from a recently serviced double-VANOS system and reinforced rear subframe mounts, addressing common chassis fatigue points. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission offers crisp engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. The suspension has been refreshed with Bilstein dampers and polyurethane bushings, maintaining its signature neutral handling balance and high-speed stability. The exterior presents well with minor patina consistent with its age, while the interior remains driver-focused and functional. A turn-key driver's car for the purist seeking performance over concours perfection.",
